{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"02e3c23f98","title":"给王枚的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7bd947cc4a","index":0,"year":1940,"month":3,"day":10,"articleId":"02e3c23f98"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e446f14a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"给王枚的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"02e3c23f98"},{"id":"9ef97bd204","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年3月10日）王枚同志：来信及代耕粮款收到了，感谢你的好意及援助。我不缺少物资，我决定把你送给我的三千五百元转送给你，作为我对你致谢的礼物，希望你接受同志的敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"02e3c23f98"},{"id":"0a70a3e326","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"02e3c23f98"},{"id":"1fcdf5bcc8","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十日1]从1939年开始，各抗日根据地军民先后开展了爱麦烈烈的大生产运动，陕甘宁边区军民每人都要参加种粮纺棉工作。毛泽东也分得一块土地进行耕种，一有时间，他就拿起头干起来。后来，由于毛泽东工作太忙，延安农民王救主动替毛泽东代料，并把代耕所得交给毛泽东。这是毛泽东给王","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"02e3c23f98"}],"page":{"id":"a6ea18ccd8","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"02e3c23f98","start":465,"end":465}}}},"__N_SSG":true}